t_msg_id":"c960952c-0cce-49bb-82dd-087d459a2aaf","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"モールス信号できそう。","ts":"1602474706.471800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"uc7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"e231e0c6-9d34-46e0-afb4-c6a7a2df9a01","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"さらに僕の場合は `C:\\` 直下に `C` という名前の `C:\\` へのシンボリックリンク貼ってるので `\"//localhost///C$/////c/c/c///////c//c/c///c\"` とか出来て便利。","ts":"1602474696.471600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"=T9R"}]},{"client_msg_id":"deb6f3a4-7769-4b63-a9ef-e1e761082108","type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"`dir \"//localhost///C$/////////Windows\"` とかも行けますが、`/` を連続してもいいのはunixもなので…","ts":"1602474451.470500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"mmR4"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b8d3be48-9fee-45f4-807c-62a51a8a3715","type":"message","user":"U7JL1UKKL","text":"きつそう","ts":"1602473545.468800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"f7o"}]},{"client_msg_id":"fa86891d-10ad-44b1-a5d8-0a7dd3b20bb7","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"いろいろ書いてると UNC サポートは難しいという話になってきた。","ts":"1602470385.468600","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"innocent","count":1,"users":["U776661HA"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"qgU2O"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b3793e47-9b1a-4c38-a335-a562bd8f1955","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"最初の `C:` に `:` が付いてる事は確認した方がいいかもですね。 `C:\\` 直下に `c` というディレクトリを作ると混乱しかねないので。","ts":"1602470355.468200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"UDnh"}]},{"client_msg_id":"268f286a-bb50-44f3-869c-a3230a8b7206","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"上記の通り、ローカルパスなのに `\u0026lt;file://C\u0026gt;:/` と `file:///C:/` の2つの実装が残念ながら存在するので、親切にするなら両方サポートしてしまうのもありかも。","ts":"1602470305.467500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ukrfr"}]},{"client_msg_id":"88959b92-2f2e-4dc8-a003-2f763dc1ef3c","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"UNIX の `/` が `//` でも行けるのと同じ理屈だろうか。","ts":"1602470193.466500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"21Zp"}]},{"client_msg_id":"11aa8ff9-f6c4-4da2-acc2-ca707ce0637c","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"ちょっと試しに\n```C:\\\u0026gt;dir \"//localhost/C$/\"\nC:\\\u0026gt;dir \"//localhost//C$/\"\nC:\\\u0026gt;dir \"//localhost///C$/\"\nC:\\\u0026gt;dir \"//localhost////C$/\"```\nしてみたら表示された。","ts":"1602470172.466100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"I4i"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c66d038a-c881-4b59-a9f0-de3cfaef9aa4","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"とはいえ Windows の UNC は透過でアクセスできるので便利。","ts":"1602469897.465400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"o7mk"}]},{"client_msg_id":"da1febf1-988b-4446-a238-a8ad8f4772fa","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"ですです。ファイルのアクセス方法が違うという事だけが言いたかったです。","ts":"1602469824.464400","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"+1","count":1,"users":["U06BRP8VD"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"EQry9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7a59eac6-42ec-41b7-af84-fc4113a47cd0","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"認証チェック画面がでるかどうか、って話かしら。","ts":"1602469731.463200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"rX7e"}]},{"client_msg_id":"40134e47-15d6-41ee-8a9d-627e55b2bbe7","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"ちなみに `\\\\localhost\\C$` はアクセスすると認証が実行されるけど `file:///C:/path/to...` は認証掛からないので、イコールとは考えない方がいいです。(釈迦説法)","ts":"1602469602.462200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"UFeQT"}]},{"client_msg_id":"00da89de-fd3e-4bcb-bcda-7c89e6bdc609","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"mattnさんの説明はちょっと混乱を招きやすいんだけど\n\n`\\\\localhost\\C$\\path\\to\\the file.txt` がUNCで\nそれを等価なURL形式で表現すると `file:///C:/path/to/the%20file.txt` になる。fileスキームのlocalhostは省略可ということで。\n\nUNCが `\\\\192.168.0.123\\C$\\path\\to\\file.txt` だったら対応するURLは `\u003cfile://192.168.0.123/C:/path/to/file.txt\u003e` になる。このURLを解釈できるUAがあるかはわかんないけど、URLの仕様上ね。","ts":"1602469369.461000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"hA5av"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a13a2cf5-fa71-4303-a94a-341e6292994e","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"書式としては `\\\\{host}\\{sharename}\\{path}` かな\n\n`{host}` にはIPアドレスも使える。\n`{path}` には `\\` が含められるけど、ほかのには入らない。","ts":"1602469160.457300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"R0vie"}]},{"client_msg_id":"53e2b3a6-e556-48d8-9040-865fd8a73bfb","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"まぁこれは意識しなくてもいいです。","ts":"1602468856.455800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"SRFO"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1bd019d3-7826-4bd0-89d3-edf4ab0095d1","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"`C$` というのは隠し共有フォルダ (`share` 部分) で見たまま `C:\\` に相当します。","ts":"1602468844.455600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"V0W"}]},{"type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"vim-molder はパスがそのまま vim と共有なので何も加工する必要もなく動く。","ts":"1602468799.454800","files":[{"id":"F01CKFLTVEY","created":1602468796,"timestamp":1602468796,"name":"image.png","title":"image.png","mimetype":"image/png","image_exif_rotation":0,"filetype":"png","pretty_type":"PNG","user":"U03C6TEAZ","mode":"hosted","editable":fa