message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"たまにローカルで2つしか付けてない実装もあるので注意。","ts":"1602468516.453500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"RHeA9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"9415c6b6-f6f3-4c21-9c09-d36b4335dd75","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"ローカルの場合に1つ多いのは Windows はボリューム名が付くので先頭が `/` じゃない、なので付ける、という感じ。","ts":"1602468479.453100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"xB8Y2"}]},{"client_msg_id":"496829cc-30d6-4cfb-a46c-9570bbbb36d9","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"ローカルパスの場合は `file:///c:/path/to/the%20file.txt` こんなの、UNC の場合はホスト名が入るので `\u003cfile://hostname/share/path/to/the%20file.txt\u003e` こんなのになります。","ts":"1602468421.452300","edited":{"user":"U03C6TEAZ","ts":"1602468554.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"/bJQ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a7272c1e-7734-4ef8-8d31-32c4bdd69dba","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"* Windows のパスは `C:\\path\\to` ですが UNC は `\\\\server\\host\\path\\to` の様に先頭に slash が2つ付く事を意識する事\n* `\\\\` や `\\\\host\\` ではファイル一覧が取れない事\nこれくらいだと思います。","ts":"1602468301.451100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"A746"}]},{"client_msg_id":"594B18EA-9EE5-4193-BE17-523FD0935B1C","type":"message","user":"U01AQ5BFNLX","text":"UNCって具体的にどんな感じで実装するんです？\nこの辺ほぼ分からないので教えて頂けると","ts":"1602467220.449500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"8YF"}]}]
